OL,6,FMr Lhermitte expanded Mon Plaisir to
OL,7,Fnew locations around London, giving
OL,8,Fcustomers an authentic French gourmet
OL,9,Fexperience.
OL,11,FIn an interview from 2007, he
OL,12,Fdescribed his restaurant as a "real
OL,13,Frestaurant for real people ` not for
OL,14,Fbullshitters".
OL,16,FEventually, Mon Plaisir found itself
OL,17,Fback down to just the original venue,
OL,18,Fand in 2011, Mr Lhermitte was
OL,19,Fdiagnosed with Alzheimer's.
