OL,4,Cauctions off decor
OL,6,FMr Lhermitte passed the restaurant
OL,7,Fover to his family in 2017 before his
OL,8,Fdeath in 2022.
OL,10,FNow Mon Plaisir is under new family
OL,11,Fownership and they're making changes.
OL,13,FA selection of the classic French
OL,14,Finterior decorations from Mon Plaisir,
OL,15,Fincluding advertising signage, art
OL,16,Fposters, clocks and cockerels, will be
OL,17,Fup for auction from December 28.
