OL,6,F"Everyone I speak to seems to have a
OL,7,FMon Plaisir story, all given with a
OL,8,Fdeep fondness- one London-based French
OL,9,Fcouple told me they loved it because
OL,10,Fit reminded them of home ` the food
OL,11,Fbeing great, the interior stylish and
OL,12,Fthe waitresses oh so rude!"
OL,14,FThe new owners are leaving the
OL,15,Foriginal 1943 dining room unaltered
OL,16,Fand keeping the copper-topped bar,
OL,17,Fsaid to have originated in a Lyon
OL,18,Fbrothel.
OL,20,FA timed auction will begin on December
OL,21,F28 and end on January 11.
